description         Pod::Markdown::Github - Convert POD to Github's specific markdown

long_description    Github flavored markdown allows for syntax highlighting \
                    using three backticks. This module inherits from \
                    Pod::Markdown and adds those backticks and an optional \
                    language identifier.

